## vim-fugitive

,gfcd
	get commit diff between current branch and develop

[/]c
	prev/next hunk
	expands inline diff
i
	next file or hunk
	expands inline diff

[/]m
	prev/next file
	collapses inline diff
(\)
	prev/next hunk
	does not expand inline diff

jump to <count>...
gu
	...untracked or unstaged file
gU
	...unstaged file
gs
	...staged file

cz?
	stash help

cm<Space>
	":Git merge "
cb<Space>
	":Git branch "
	shows branches in window

# tmux

*panes* are splits within *windows*

---

## Commands

:move-window -r
		renumber windows

:select-layout even-{ horizontal | vertical }
		split pane sizes evenly horizontally/vertically

:splitw -f{ h | v }
		create pane spanning full window height/width

:join-pane -s <src> -t <target>

:list-commands

---

## Shortcuts

Alt + { 1 | 2 }
		split pane sizes evenly horizontally/vertically

&/x		kill curr window/pane
L/l/;	last session/window/pane

i		display msg
~		show msgs
t		time
?		list hotkeys
!		break pane into window

<Space>
		next pane layout

# Stash

staging info is not stored in stash commits

git stash [push]
			stash changes to tracked files
			revert changes to tracked files, staged or not

	--keep-index
			stash changes to tracked files
			revert changes to unstaged tracked files

	--include-untracked
			stash changes to tracked and untracked files
			revert changes to all files, staged or unstaged, tracked or untracked

git show stash@{n}^3
			show any untracked files in a stash commit

---

git clean
		delete untracked files
git reset
		revert tracked changes

git reset <commit>
		undoes all changes after <commit>
		preserves the changes locally

git reset --hard <commit>
		undoes all changes after <commit>
		discards the reverted changes

		discards all history and changes back to <commit>
